<section>
<title>Ǩii ton leäk?</title>

<p>
<em class="focus">Answer the following questions and tell about yourself. Use the <a href="http://victorio-old.uit.no/webdict/index_eng-sms.html">dictionary</a> for looking up the names in Skolt Sámi.</em> 
</p>

<p><em class="lg_mat">Ǩii ton leäk?</em> _ _ _ _</p>
<p><em class="lg_mat">Mij lij tuu famiˊlja?</em> _ _ _ _</p>
<p><em class="lg_mat">Mii lij tuu eeˊjj nõmm?</em> _ _ _ _</p>
<p><em class="lg_mat">Mii lij tuu jieˊnn nõmm?</em> _ _ _ _</p>
<p><em class="lg_mat">Mâiˊd ton tuejjääk?</em> _ _ _ _</p>
<p><em class="lg_mat">Koˊst ton leäk tuejast?</em> _ _ _ _</p>
<p><em class="lg_mat">Mâiˊd tuu eˊčč tuejjad?</em> _ _ _ _</p>
<p><em class="lg_mat">Mâiˊd tuu jeäˊnn tuejjad?</em> _ _ _ _</p>

<p>
